"Hello everyone. Today, I am presenting my project called GovtScheme.AI.

The Problem: There are many government schemes available, but they are hard to find. People don't know which schemes they qualify for because the rules are too complicated.

The Solution: GovtScheme.AI makes finding government schemes easy and smart.

Our project has three main features:

Scheme Finder: You input your age, income, and job, and it instantly shows you only the schemes you are eligible for.
Scheme Mitra (AI Chatbot): A helpful chat assistant. You can chat with it in English or Tamil, and it will recommend the best schemes for you.
Explorer & Compare: You can search through schemes and compare them side-by-side.
Technology Used:

ReactJS for a fast and beautiful frontend.
NodeJS & Express for the backend server.
Vanilla CSS for the modern frosted-glass design.
GitHub & Vercel to host the website online.
In short, this project helps common people find and apply for the right government schemes in just a few clicks.

Thank you!
